# ChatGPT-like Django Backend

API-only Django/DRF backend for Web Programming Homework 3. It includes JWT auth, account linking and switching, user-owned projects and conversations, mock AI replies, public/private assistants, AI model entitlement checks, subscription quota enforcement, protected attachments, Swagger docs, seed data, and a meaningful Django test suite.

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.13 recommended for this workspace
- SQLite, via Python's standard library
- No frontend or external AI API is required

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py seed_demo
python manage.py runserver
```

Swagger UI:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/docs/
```

OpenAPI schema:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/schema/
```

Health check:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/health/
```

## Tests

```bash
python manage.py test
```

The suite covers auth/JWT, ownership isolation, model and assistant permissions, account linking/switching, subscription upgrades, free-tier quota, premium bypass, message send/edit/delete, protected attachments, soft delete, project cascade deletion, health, Swagger, and structured errors.

## Demo Data

Seed demo data with:

```bash
python manage.py seed_demo
```

