| Admin/Premium | `admin_demo` | `admin@example.com` | `DemoPass123!` |
| Free user | `free_demo` | `free@example.com` | `DemoPass123!` |
| Premium user | `premium_demo` | `premium@example.com` | `DemoPass123!` |

